title: [Grawood Farmstead, Maze]
description: The smell of the soil here is heady and rich and the ground is slightly damp.  Rows of corn are arranged in a neat and orderly fashion, lined up like soldiers standing shoulder to shoulder on a battlefield.  Their sashes of yellow silk hang limply from their husks, damp and lifeless.
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
